{"abstract": "Jeroen van der Veer deftly righted the oil major after an accounting scandal. His successor, Peter Voser, will continue the company\u2019s overhaul.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/29/business/global/29oil.html", "snippet": "Jeroen van der Veer deftly righted the oil major after an accounting scandal. His successor, Peter Voser, will continue the company\u2019s overhaul.", "lead_paragraph": "When Jeroen van der Veer took the helm of Royal Dutch Shell five years ago, the company was mired in an accounting scandal involving its reporting of oil and gas reserves, a flap that nearly ended its century-long independence. Mr. van der Veer revamped Shell\u2019s notoriously complex corporate structure, merged its fractious English and Dutch entities, and eventually restored trust with governments, regulators and investors. ", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2009/06/29/business/global/29oil_600.jpg", "height": 361, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2009/06/29/business/global/29oil_600.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 361}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2009/06/29/business/global/29oil_75.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2009/06/29/business/global/29oil_75.jpg", "thumbnailwidth": 75, "thumbnailheight": 75}}], "headline": {"main": "Shell Faces Even More Revamping", "kicker": null, "content_kicker": null, "print_headline": "Shell Faces Even More Revamping", "name": null, "seo": null, "sub": null}, "keywords": [{"name": "subject", "value": "Oil (Petroleum) and Gasoline", "rank": 1, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "Royal Dutch Shell Plc", "rank": 2, "major": "N"}